    "desc": "Voted Best Restaurant in Annapolis, Soul is inspired by the flavors of New Orleans, the Delta, the Carolinas and our home state of Maryland.",
    "navbar": "Home\nMenu\nSoul @Home\nProhibition Mixes\nLive Music\nMore",
    "text": "509 S. Cherry Grove, Annapolis, MD 21403\nOrder Online Now\n0\nLog In\nHome\nMenu\nSoul @Home\nProhibition Mixes\nLive Music\nMore\nHome\n  Southern Cuisine\nLocal Hospitality\n Our Philosophy\nWe believe a meal is as much about the people as it is about the food.  From Southern classics to modern flare, we are inspired by the flavors and people of the Carolinas, the Delta, New Orleans and our home town Annapolis, MD.\nArtfully designed small plates encourage our guests to share a meal as you would at home. Whether a weekend brunch on the garden patio, a family dinner or happy hour with friends, we look forward to sharing our Soul with you.\n509 S. Cherry Grove, Annapolis, MD 21403\n410-267-6191\n All Day Menu\nSeasonal dishes, bold flavors and healthy options \nSee Menu >\nSoul At Home\nEnjoy Soul's entire menu and special family meals at home.\nOrder Now >\nProhibition\nMixes\nInnovative cocktails that mix the old and the new now available to enjoy at home.\nSee Menu >\nOur Partners\nBringing the best of Maryland and the Mid-Atlantic Farmers, Growers, Brewers, and Bakers\nLiberty Delight Farm\nPapa John's Farm\nMise En Place Farm\nMikeGrow Greens\nBlades Orchard\nAnne Arundel County Farmers Market\nSee Menus >\n Hours\nMonday thru Wednesday  -  Closed \nThursday thru Saturday  -  4 pm  to 9 pm\nSunday - 11 am to 6 pm\n Let's Connect\n  509 S. Cherry Grove, Annapolis, MD 21403     |     410-267-6191     |       hello@soulannapolis.com\n  \"Hidden Gem in Annapolis\"\n@russellh197, Baltimore\n\"The very SOUL of Southern Cooking\"\n@AGMAT, Annapolis\n\"Do yourself a favor and go to SOUL immediately!\"\nAmy G, Annapolis\n Back to Top\n© 2018 Blue Bistro, LLC",
